BY INSTALLING, USING, REGISTERING TO OR OTHERWISE ACCESSING THE SERVICES, YOU AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY AND GIVE AN EXPLICIT AND INFORMED CONSENT TO THE PROCESSING OF YOUR PERSONAL DATA IN ACCORDANCE WITH THIS PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY, PLEASE DO NOT INSTALL, USE, REGISTER TO OR OTHERWISE ACCESS THE SERVICES. Anas asim lamloum reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at reasonable times, so please review it frequently. If Anas asim lamloum makes material or significant changes to this Privacy Policy, Anas asim lamloum may post a notice on Anas asim lamloum website along with the updated Privacy Policy. Your continued use of Services will signify your acceptance of the changes to this Privacy Policy.



Non-personal data



For purposes of this Privacy Policy, “non-personal data” means information that does not directly identify you. The types of non-personal data Anas asim lamloum may collect and use include, but are not limited to: application properties, including, but not limited to application name, package name and icon installed on your device. Your checkin (include like, recommendation) of a game will be disclosed to all Anas asim lamloum users.



Anas asim lamloum may use and disclose to Person1 ’s partners and contractors the collected non-personal data for purposes of analyzing usage of the Services, advertisement serving, managing and providing the Services and to further develop the Services and other Anas asim lamloum services and products.



You recognize and agree that the analytics companies utilized by Anas asim lamloum may combine the information collected with other information they have independently collected from other services or products relating to your activities. These companies collect and use information under their own privacy policies.



