Google Analytics is an analysis service provided by Google Inc. Google utilizes the collected data to track and examine the use of Anas asim lamloum Apps, to prepare reports on user activities and share them with other Google services. Google may use the data to contextualize and personalize the ads of its own advertising network. (http://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/)



